---
title: Double-Stacked Italian Beef Burgers with Caramelized Onions and Parmesan Potato Wedges
description: Get your napkins ready – this is one seriously juicy burger! We've loaded it with flavour, from the caramelized onions to the Italian mayo to the Parmesan potato wedges, so that every bite will take you to your happy place.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-beef-burgers-a1091e5f.jpg
